    &lt;CommentText&gt;Thank you for your feedback posted on the NHS website. Rachel Hassey, Emergency Department Operations Manager, Manchester Royal Infirmary (MRI) would like to apologise for your long wait, however was pleased to hear that your experience with our professional medical team was positive at the on the 2nd July 2019.

Rachel would like to apologise that you found the chairs uncomfortable and would like to make you aware that we have new chairs on order, due to arrive in the near future. We will also be looking into offering better refreshment facilities for all patients waiting and will consider the ideas for TV programmes.

It is important to us that comments are heard and seen as an opportunity for the service to make changes and improvements wherever possible.

The Patient Experience Team&lt;/CommentText&gt;
